702991f-a.title: Brooklyn: Anchorage Place - Plymouth Street
702991f-a.text:
Anchorage Place (Beyond fense, cars thereon) between Plymouth
itreet (left) and Water Street (riccht). The 6 story building at
the right houses the Liand H.Stern Co. At the right is a partial
view of the Manhattan Bridge Tower.
April 4, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
